---
import SectionHeading from '@/components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="about page-shell" id="about">
  <SectionHeading eyebrow="About" title="A voice for spiritual clarity and disciplined leadership." />
  <div class="about__grid">
    <div class="about__copy">
      <p>
        Prophet Selasi Adrah serves with a mandate to help people discern
        purpose, deepen devotion, and lead with spiritual conviction. His
        ministry blends prophetic insight with practical teaching for daily
        decisions, family life, business, and calling.
      </p>
      <p>
        This platform exists as a clear entry point for appointments,
        ministry updates, events, giving, and moments from the work.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about__stats" aria-label="Ministry focus areas">
      <article>
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Prophetic Counsel</h3>
        <p>Private guidance for people seeking prayerful direction.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Kingdom Teaching</h3>
        <p>Messages shaped for faith, purpose, leadership, and growth.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Gatherings</h3>
        <p>Events that create space for worship, prayer, and encounter.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
